There are a total of 2^3 = 8 states.

000 - (Unreal) - black
001 - (Single) - red
010 - (Single) - green
011 - (Mixed) - yellow
100 - (Single) - blue
101 - (Mixed) - magneta
110 - (Mixed) - cyan
111 - (Unreal) - white

Deciding states
We decide the state based on a threshold. We can keep this as 0.1 (post g/k normalization).

